WEBVTT

00:00:01.291 --> 00:00:03.214
IM HANITSOLET

00:00:03.214 --> 00:00:04.792
HAGEVERET ZELBST

00:00:04.792 --> 00:00:05.844
FANYA.

00:00:06.778 --> 00:00:08.577
ikh bin geblibn lebn

00:00:08.972 --> 00:00:11.311
ober ikh farges nit mayne poyerim

00:00:11.470 --> 00:00:13.118
vos hobn mir geholfn

00:00:13.258 --> 00:00:15.479
tsu derlebn di frayheyt

00:00:16.785 --> 00:00:17.808
zey hobn in mir

00:00:18.220 --> 00:00:20.138
ayngekritst in hartsn.

00:00:20.278 --> 00:00:23.394
der elter dor iz shoyn geshtorbn, zaynen nito.

00:00:23.535 --> 00:00:26.381
ober zeyere kinder zaynen geblibn

00:00:27.214 --> 00:00:30.954
un ikh hob mit zey haynt a gute, a groyse farbindung

00:00:30.977 --> 00:00:34.129
un a dank di kinder bin ikh take geblibn lebn.

00:00:34.129 --> 00:00:36.084
az zey hobn nit dertseylt

00:00:36.310 --> 00:00:37.941
in shule far z-

00:00:37.997 --> 00:00:39.572
vos zey UNK gegangen

00:00:39.572 --> 00:00:41.282
in der tsayt fun der SHOA

00:00:41.322 --> 00:00:43.082
az bay zey oyfn oyvn

00:00:43.082 --> 00:00:46.516
oder bay zey tsvishn di khazeyrim mit di beheymes

00:00:46.516 --> 00:00:49.553
gefint zikh un se bahalt zikh oys a yidishe meydl

00:00:49.553 --> 00:00:51.964
az zey hobn gekent haltn dem sod

00:00:53.860 --> 00:00:56.489
vos iz zeyer a groyse zakh hobn zey oyfgeton

00:00:56.489 --> 00:00:58.241
un ikh ken dos nit fargesn

00:00:59.023 --> 00:01:01.548
iz az ikh bin gekumen do in Yisroel

00:01:01.555 --> 00:01:03.827
un do iz aroys a nayer UNK

00:01:03.934 --> 00:01:06.529
un in ale tsaytungen geshribn geven

00:01:06.529 --> 00:01:09.584
az di velkhe hobn oysgebahaltn yidn

00:01:09.584 --> 00:01:12.360
kumt zey tsvantsik oder draysik dolar.

00:01:12.360 --> 00:01:15.150
hob ikh ongehoybn zeyer arbetn vegn dem

00:01:15.966 --> 00:01:18.964
shoyn do tsvey mishpokhes vos zey lebn in Poyln

00:01:19.493 --> 00:01:22.440
un akurat dan in yener tsayt iz geven

00:01:22.513 --> 00:01:25.050
LECH WALESA UNK in Poyln

00:01:25.050 --> 00:01:28.140
un ikh hob im gegebn a briv, un ikh hob im gebetn

00:01:28.140 --> 00:01:31.070
az er zol bagegenen zikh mit mayne mishpokhes

00:01:31.070 --> 00:01:32.480
un er zol oykh

00:01:32.757 --> 00:01:34.534
zey anerkenen

00:01:34.534 --> 00:01:36.398
az zey zaynen CHASIM-

00:01:36.398 --> 00:01:38.187
CH- CHASIDEI UMOT

00:01:38.187 --> 00:01:39.132
OLAM

00:01:39.132 --> 00:01:41.512
oyf poylish heyst es SPRAWIEDLIWYCH

00:01:41.512 --> 00:01:43.849
un er hot dos mir zeyer geholfn.

00:01:43.849 --> 00:01:46.211
er hot aroysgerufn mayne mishpokhes.

00:01:46.211 --> 00:01:47.966
er hot zey gegebn azoyne

00:01:47.966 --> 00:01:50.992
dokumentn, dos heyst papirn

00:01:50.992 --> 00:01:52.822
az zey hobn oysgebahaltn yidn

00:01:52.822 --> 00:01:55.352
un zey hobn haynt tsu draysik dolar

00:01:55.403 --> 00:01:56.741
yedn monat

00:01:56.741 --> 00:02:00.081
der fond iz nit fun Poyln un nit fun YISRAEL.

00:02:00.081 --> 00:02:01.691
dos iz nor fun Amerike

00:02:01.691 --> 00:02:03.888
dos iz an internatsyonaler fond

00:02:03.888 --> 00:02:07.457
vos git far alemen, far di frantseyzn, far di holender

00:02:07.457 --> 00:02:11.118
far ale mentshn velkhe hobn oysgehaltn yidn.

00:02:11.118 --> 00:02:13.807
di bakumen haynt draysik dolar

00:02:13.932 --> 00:02:16.806
a monat un hobn groyse rekht

00:02:16.806 --> 00:02:18.279
oyf andere zakhn.

00:02:18.420 --> 00:02:20.315
tsvishn di mishpokhes

00:02:20.315 --> 00:02:23.122
velkhe ikh fir haynt a korespondents

00:02:23.466 --> 00:02:24.489
iz do

00:02:25.356 --> 00:02:28.286
eyne lebt i- in Pe- Sankt Peterburg

00:02:29.322 --> 00:02:31.019
eyne iz do

00:02:31.465 --> 00:02:32.618
in Poyln.

00:02:32.618 --> 00:02:35.222
di tsveyte iz nit lang geshtorbn.

00:02:36.105 --> 00:02:38.338
zeyere eltern velkhe

00:02:38.338 --> 00:02:43.844
in, in tsvey un fertsikstn, f- dray un fertsikstn, fir un fertsikstn, ven ikh bin bay zey geven

00:02:44.256 --> 00:02:46.629
hobn zey mir oysgeshtrekt di hant

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:50.122
un zeyer lebn iz geven in a groyse sakone

00:02:50.415 --> 00:02:52.434
tsulib mir, der yidishke

00:02:52.626 --> 00:02:54.577
un zey hobn dos oysgehaltn

00:02:55.427 --> 00:02:57.176
ober zey zaynen shoyn nito.

00:02:57.469 --> 00:03:00.326
iz di mishpokhes vil ikh take dermonen

00:03:00.326 --> 00:03:02.309
es zol blaybn fareybikt

00:03:02.309 --> 00:03:04.191
az s'iz geven in yener tsayt

00:03:04.191 --> 00:03:07.338
gute kristns velkhe hobn oysgehaltn yidn.

00:03:07.338 --> 00:03:08.755
khotsh nit keyn sakh

00:03:08.755 --> 00:03:11.413
ober ver iz geblibn an eydes fun der historye?

00:03:11.413 --> 00:03:12.920
vil ikh oysrekhenen

00:03:13.467 --> 00:03:14.861
eyn mishpokhe

00:03:15.559 --> 00:03:18.033
SZYDLOWSKI DIMITRI un ⟨SHURA⟩

00:03:18.546 --> 00:03:20.649
vos zeyer tokhter heyst

00:03:20.942 --> 00:03:23.366
MARIA un lebt in Sankt Peter-

00:03:23.558 --> 00:03:26.302
-burg. a mol hot zi geheysn Leningrad.

00:03:26.410 --> 00:03:28.159
di tsveyte mishpokhe

00:03:28.317 --> 00:03:30.066
ikh bin geven oysgebahaltn

00:03:30.190 --> 00:03:32.985
iz geven KODIS JOZEF

00:03:33.767 --> 00:03:35.904
zeyer tokhter iz MARIA.

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:39.566
di drite mishpokhe

00:03:39.724 --> 00:03:41.557
KODIS BOLESLAW

00:03:42.610 --> 00:03:44.460
oykh a tokhter MARIA.

00:03:46.221 --> 00:03:49.303
di MARIA iz shoyn geshtorbn in Poyln.

00:03:50.018 --> 00:03:52.816
a ferte mishpokhe hob ikh vos lebt

00:03:52.816 --> 00:03:54.360
haynt in Polotsk

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:56.157
vos oykh oyf Vaysrusland

00:03:56.157 --> 00:03:58.145
di familye heyst MEJZA.

00:03:58.320 --> 00:04:00.086
di muter iz geshtorbn.

00:04:00.396 --> 00:04:01.655
di tokhter

00:04:01.712 --> 00:04:03.481
shraybt zikh mit mir durkh

00:04:03.481 --> 00:04:06.097
nor mer shraybt zikh mit mir durkh an eynikl.

00:04:06.097 --> 00:04:07.759
nit ikh ken ir

00:04:07.759 --> 00:04:10.619
nit zi ken mir, mir hobn zikh keyn mol nit getrofn

00:04:10.619 --> 00:04:12.070
nor zi shraybt mir

00:04:12.070 --> 00:04:14.568
DOROGAYA BABUSHKA FANYA, dos heyst

00:04:14.568 --> 00:04:15.662
tayere

00:04:16.039 --> 00:04:20.145
bobe Fanye. mit ir hob ikh a noente farbindung

00:04:20.145 --> 00:04:23.824
khotsh ikh ken ir nit, ober zi veyst az ir bobe

00:04:23.824 --> 00:04:27.154
hot mir oysgebahaltn, un a dank ir bobn leb ikh.

00:04:28.797 --> 00:04:29.955
TODA RABA

00:04:30.130 --> 00:04:30.934
GEVERET FANYA.

00:04:30.433 --> 00:04:35.070
ot dos hob ikh oyfgeton far mayn lebn khotsh vos mayne gute poyerim

00:04:35.070 --> 00:04:37.560
zaynen CHASIDEI UMOT

00:04:37.560 --> 00:04:38.409
OLAM.

00:04:38.449 --> 00:04:39.455
ven ikh v-

00:04:39.462 --> 00:04:42.983
volt kenen, volt ikh zey aynladn tsu zikh in Yisroel

00:04:43.225 --> 00:04:45.176
khotsh oyf a, a monat tsayt

00:04:45.182 --> 00:04:47.187
bavayzn zey YAD VASHEM

00:04:47.187 --> 00:04:48.461
bavayzn zey

00:04:48.461 --> 00:04:51.521
vi es zet oys Yerusholaim, di heylike shtot

00:04:51.595 --> 00:04:55.132
di Kat- vos do. ale kirkhes zaynen do fun BETLECHEM

00:04:55.132 --> 00:04:59.290
nor tsum badoyern bin ikh nit imshtand zey tsu brengen mir tsu gest.

